  body
    header(class='header active' role="header")
      div(class="logo")
      h1(class="wow fadeIn title") Amazing photography
      h2(class="wow fadeInDown subtitle") from your Dropbox
      div(class="action")
        if invited
          p We'll reach you when the beta is launched
        else
          form(action="/join" method="post")
            div(class="buttons")
              input(type="text" autofocus='true' placeholder='you@ro.ck' name='email')
              button(type="submit") Signup for Beta

    section(class='features')
      div(class='feature wow fadeInLeft')
        div(class='thumb')
          i(class='ion-images')
        div(class='description')
          h2(class='title') Your photos are always with you
        | Using Dropbox means that your photos always stay with you, in the same
        | resolution. Stop worrying about losing your photos, they never leave
        | the safety of your Dropbox.

      div(class='feature wow fadeInLeft')
        div(class='thumb')
          i(class='ion-upload')
        div(class='description')
          h2(class='title') No more upload forms
        | Upload that stunning photo of mountains you have visited last
        | weekend by just pasting it in your local Dropbox folder.
        | Stop wasting time on uploads and take more amazing photos instead!

      div(class='feature wow fadeInLeft')
        div(class='thumb')
          i(class='ion-ionic')
        div(class='description')
          h2(class='title') Simplicity at its finest
        | Our interface is very simple and easy to use. We strongly value
        | minimalism and we're focused to make photo sharing fun and simple again.

     footer(class='action')
       if invited
         p Thanks for your support
       else
         h2 Join the party, take your early access seat
         form(action="/join" method="post")
           div(class="buttons")
             input(type="text" placeholder='you@ro.ck' name='email')
             button(type="submit") Signup for Beta
